        "description": "Operator action: grant the chosen permission level to a Matrix user on this realm. Pick from existing users (sourced from the `users` table) or type a new Matrix ID like `@user:matrix.host`. POSTs to the realm-server with `Authorization: Bearer ${grafana_secret}` (token from SSM at apply time, CS-10929).",
